de.weltraumschaf.jvfs.impl

Class JvfsDefaultFileSystemProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.nio.file.spi.FileSystemProvider
      • de.weltraumschaf.jvfs.impl.JvfsDefaultFileSystemProvider

  • public class JvfsDefaultFileSystemProvider
extends FileSystemProvider
    A provider implementation which is registered as default file system. Via JvfsFileSystems you can mount virtual in memory file systems. This provider will dispatches all paths matching a mounted file system to JvfsFileSystemProvider.
    Author:
    Sven Strittmatter
